data.meta_description: Wood Library - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides a catalog of items from the library of Anthony Wood. It lists 23 entries, with details for each including title, publication information, notes on condition, and reference numbers. The entries cover a range of works from the 15th-17th centuries on diverse topics including history, religion, and literature.
